Week 2 - OpenFramework Project


What I Learning

1. OpenFrameworks project structure (main, ofApp)
2. How to use ofxMaxim in openFrameworks for creating sound and music systems.
3. Learn the basics of 2D graphics in openFrameworks by drawing geometric primitives and striped patterns
4. Adding a GUI and Handling Keyboard Events


Learning Materials

